						Joins
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Benefits of Breaking Data into Tables
	Efficient storage
	Easier manipulation
	Greater scalability
	Logically models a process
	Tables are related through common valuse(keys)

it is important to know the JOIN is not a phisical entity, in other words it does not create anything perminent, it only exist duration of ther query execution to help you get that information you're trying to get..
there are severel types of Joins
